0ZjQxMzM4MWI1NzdiMTgzZDcyMDozMjEyOjJjMWU5NWJjMzM1NzdjODk4MDcxNjk0ODI5MmE3ZDIyOmh0dHBALy9lYzItMy0xMzQtODYtMTc1LnVzLWVhc3QtMi5jb21wdXRlLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb206MA==\",\"sections\":{\"description\":\"<p>Add an inquiry button on every WooCommerce product page and the shop archive page.<\\/p>\\n\",\"changelog\":\"<p>6.3.5 (28-11-2019)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Compatibility with WooCommerce 3.8.1 and WordPress 5.3.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Multivendor Beta support using Dokan Multivendor.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.3.4 (20-08-2019)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature:\\u00a0Compatibility with WooCommerce 3.7.0.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added settings in the General tab to enable\\/ disable Price and Remarks columns in enquiry mail and enquiry cart.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added settings in the Display tab to style and position the enquiry cart icon.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added setting in the General tab to modify the Remarks column name.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added setting to disable bootstrap on frontend.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added setting to manually provide the selector to fetch the variation Id on the single variable product page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added JS trigger event to extend PEP functionality when enquiry form is submitted successfully.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: An Enquiry button is enabled only when a variation is selected on Variable Product page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Modified the phone field in the custom form.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Product attributes issue in enquiry cart for non-English language.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Rating field validation issue on quote creation page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Rating fields preview not visible on form edit page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Enquiry edit page issue after an enquiry is anonymized.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Translation issues for enquiry and quote listing on the myaccount page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: JS error on mobile view of an enquiry cart when enquiry mail and enquiry cart templates are overridden.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Quantity field issue when product price or \'Add to cart\' is disabled.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Conditional logic issue based on Rating field in the custom form.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Depended fields were not getting visible after changing the value of the \'select\' field.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.3.3 (09-05-2019)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Compatibility with WooCommerce 3.6.2.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Getting date field as \'undefined\' in the customer enquiry email.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Alignment of \'Remarks\' field in the customer enquiry email.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.3.2 (14-03-2019)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Added compatibility with Captcha V3 for PEP forms.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Not able to submit enquiry when conditional Login contains metacharacters.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Send Quotation <strong>Form<\\/strong> is always filled with Admin\'s Info (For Custom Forms).<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: JS error on the enquiry edit page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: JS error on quote creation page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Order Placed from Quotation shows the selected language\'s product in Dashboard order.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Removed conditional logic from Captcha field.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Rating field issues in custom form.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.3.1 (02-01-2019)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Compatibility with caching.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Database Session based Enquiry Cart.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: The variation price is not displayed in Single variable product page when the variation is selected and \'Show price\' is disabled for any of the related product.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Not getting variations in search result while creating quote if any variable product is not in use.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Custom Form Field Icon size is larger than the field height.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Conditional Logic not working for Single Product Enquiry Forms.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: The Form, when moved to the drafts, was getting displayed while making an enquiry. Now the state of selected enquiry form cannot be changed.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: If the Product does not have a price and is added to quote,\\u00a0 the purchase was not possible, the products are purchasable now.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.3.0 (14-08-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Quote history is now displayed on the frontend on my account page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Solved session related warning messages when using PHP version 7.0+.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: In the admin backend, hover over the \'customer\' field on the enquiry edit page to see the entire customer data.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: JS compatibility of the function \'showAlerts\' with IE11.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Issue with the multiple file upload fields in the enquiry form.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: When the label of a field is changed while creating the custom form, then reflected label does not appear in the conditional logic drop-down.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Checkbox issue on \'Create New Quote\' page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Issue when saving the name and email in the browser for custom enquiry forms.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: \'Enquiry sent\' success message issue in case of single product enquiry.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: \'Date\' field issue in case of Single Product Enquiry and Default Form.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: If \'Terms and Conditions\' setting is not enabled, then don\'t add \'[customer@email] accepted the Enquiry terms and conditions.\' in the email.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Don\'t verify nonce if \'Disable Nonce\' setting is enabled.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Translation Issues.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.2.2 (12-06-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Out of Stock issue when there are many variations in the single variable product.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Issue with checkout when WPML is active.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.2.1 (25-05-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Added privacy policy suggestion text on privacy policy page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Added note on the\\u00a0custom form edit page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Solved settings issue for versions below WordPress 4.7<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.2.0 (24-05-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Enquiries data is included in export personal data.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Enquiries data is anonymized during remove personal data.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Bulk action to remove personal data of one or more enquiry.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Variation slug displayed on cart page instead of variation name.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Email Mobile responsive.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.1.0 (03-04-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Setting to allow only logged in users to make an\\u00a0enquiry<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Setting to avoid the nonce issue<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Templates for enquiry cart, enquiry emails and approval rejection page<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Prefilled name and email in custom form if the user is logged in<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Issue with multiple lines thank you message in the custom form<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Issue with google analytics in the custom form<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.6 (23-03-2018)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li id=\\\":ez1.ma\\\" class=\\\"Mu SP\\\" title=\\\"23 February 2018 at 17:58:44 UTC+5:30\\\" data-tooltip=\\\"23 February 2018 at 17:58:44 UTC+5:30\\\"><span id=\\\":ez1.co\\\" class=\\\"tL8wMe EMoHub\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\u00a0Fix: Solved the issue with quotation price not applying in some case.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.5<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Changed the position of modal to solve the modal overlay issue<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.4<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Minor bug fixes related to Custom Form<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.3<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Solved issue with Bootstrap.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Solved issue with same class name in some cases for custom form.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.2<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Solved a minor issue with conditional logic<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.1<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Support with Google Analytics. Per Product Enquiry tracking<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Conditional Logic bug resolved<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Custom Form is now Translation Ready<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: \'Send me a Copy\' added to Custom Form<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Other minor bug fixes<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: All emails from the plugin are now mobile responsive<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>6.0.0<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Solved issues with PHP 7<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added a new Form Builder for easy adding, deleting and changing fields<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>5.0.0<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Improvement: Restructured Database: Created a new table \\u2018enquiry_products\\u2019 and migrated old details to the new one.<\\/li>\\n<li>Improvement: Made Enquiry Edit Page, Create Quote Page and Enquiry Cart Page Responsive<\\/li>\\n<li>Improvement: Refactored the Code<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>4.5.0<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Added Google ReCaptcha to the form to prevent spam<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Added Search Field on the enquiry listing page to quick search a particular client or quote request<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Hide the filters on enquiry listing page when there are no enquiries of that type under it<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Display number of new enquiries on enquiry listing page<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Jump to checkout page when clicked on approve. No need to enter the email address associated with the quote request with the condition that quote is approved by clicking on the link in the email and not the pdf.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Made the floating enquiry cart baloon sticky<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: In the email settings, if \\u2018Mail to Admin\\u2019 and\\/or \\u2018Mail to Author\\u2019 is checked, then allow user to save email setting without any email address in the recipient field<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Removed telephone number validation to support all kinds of telephone number formats.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>4.4.0<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Feature: Attach Button on form which allows sending files to admin<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Having a PDF Quote as an attachment in the email sent to customers is now optional. Quotation will be displayed in the email body with link to checkout page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Feature: Screen Options added to set the number of items on enquiry listing page.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Allow adding a second variation to the enquiry cart after the first one has been added.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: New and improved enquiry email template<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Common template for Single and Multiproduct enquiry emails.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Create templating of Email Table.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Text changes for ease of understanding.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Browser page title changed to \'edit enquiry\' for ease of switching back to the right tab.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Fixed WPML compatibility issues<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Stored enquiry language as site language even when WPML is not activated to avoid future compatibility issues.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Fixed minor loading issuess.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: 500 Characters Remaining text now translation ready.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>4.3.1<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>\\nFeature: Now Compatible with php7+<\\/li>\\n<li>\\nImprovement: Text changes made for better understanding\\n<\\/li>\\n<li>\\nBug Fixes Post WooCommerce 3.0 Release:\\n<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Add to cart issue on WooCommerce 3.0 resolved. Button now being hidden when disabled through bulk actions<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Font Color on single product enquiry can be changed<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Quantity now being sent in the enquiry email to the admin<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Variable product price now being applied according to price in quotation<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Decimal numbers will not be accepted in quantity field<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Subject being sent twice if field left blank, now resolved<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Variable Product Prices weren\'t being displayed after WooCommerce 3.0 update, now resolved.<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Price validation on create quote page. Negative prices will not be accepted now.<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix:\\u00a0Quantity Validation in Create Quote Page. Negative values will not be accepted now.<\\/li>\\n<li>Bug Fix: Solved all other validation issues.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">4.3.0<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Feature: Create New Quote from Dashboard.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Fea