<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":24} -->\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Rug Cleaning Coral Gables These are the only parties with whom we may possibly share your information with:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>We may share user content and your personal information which may include usage data device identifiers, information from cookies, location data, and log files. These are applicable only to businesses that are legally part of the same group of companies that Grand Oriental Rug Gallery is part of and Affiliates. Affiliates may use this information to help provide, understand, and improve Grand Oriental Rug Gallery services and affiliates\' own services. These fine affiliates will respect your choices when you decide who is allowed to look at your photographs.</li><li>We may also share certain data such as cookies with our partners involved in third party advertising. This will let third-party advertising networks to deliver targeted ads that they think you would be interested in, among other things.</li><li>Our company may also share your info as well as those from tools like location data, cookies, device identifiers and log files, with third-party companies that help us in providing the services to you. Access to your information will be permitted as long as the third party agrees to our terms of confidentiality.</li><li> We may take out some of the information that is identifiable to you and share the unidentified data with other parties. Grand Oriental Rug Gallery may also combine your info with other data in a way that it is no longer identified and share that as anonymous information.</li><li> You are not allowed to create links to any page of Grand Oriental Rug Gallery’s website unless you get a written consent from us. You may do so but it will be at your own risk.</li><li>Grand Oriental Rug Galler