.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Current condition – One of the main points to consider is the condition of your rugs. Ideally, if they are in a high-traffic area, they should be cleaned at least every 18 months. For accidents, make sure to contact us or bring your rug in ASAP – the sooner we receive it, the greater the chances we can eliminate any stains or other concerns to get your rug looking great.</li><li>Repairs – repairing a small area today offsets the problems a larger one may cause in the future. We will inform you before cleaning your rugs if we discover any areas of concern and suggest any subsequent course of action. We specialize in all types of repairs and restorations.<br>Experience – we have served the Brickell area since the days of Miami Vice – long before skyscrapers and condos graced the skyline, and when Brickell Avenue was a two lane street. We are familiar with issues affecting the coastal community, and were one of the first to respond following Hurricane Irma.</li><li>Animals and family size – While we love our pets and children, their messes are another story. We get it, spills happen, dirt gets tracked in, “accidents” happen. So rely on the experts to wash them out. Our extensive knowledge on what works propels us to address any issues immediately and effectively.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nSome of these points to consider are overlooked, but it is important to consider the myriad of secondary factors that can affect the cleaning of your carpet.<br>We offer pick-up and delivery service Monday through Saturday. Simply call 305 442 4500 Or 305 490 1936.<br>Brickell is an affluent urban neighborhood located near downtown Miami. It is often dubbed the ‘financial district of Miami’ due to the presence of many international banks and investment firms. It is hosts many of the tallest skyscrapers in Miami and Florida, as well as the site of many foreign consulates. Named after the area’s main avenue, Brickell is also famous for its shops, restaurants, high rises, and the new mall, Brickell City Centre.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Brickell','','inherit','closed','closed','','623-autosave-v1','','','2019-12-17 04:04:24','2019-12-17 04:04:24','',623,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/623-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(846,1,'2019-12-17 04:10:32','2019-12-17 04:10:32','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> When you need carpet cleaning services in Key Biscayne that you should always go to the experts. This is essential when it comes to expensive items like oriental rugs since experts would know what would be the best chemical and agents to use on it. We at Grand Oriental Rug Gallery will ensure that everything is done right. We have years of experience in carpet and rugs cleaning in Key Biscayne.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim-NaN has-background-dim\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"placeholder\":\"Write title…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Key Biscayne</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Why Hire Us?:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As with anything you own, you want to ensure that those whom you entrust with your valuables, are both professional and skilled at what they do. When it comes to Oriental rug cleaning services, it’s no different.<br>When it comes to rug cleaners in Key Biscayne, look no further than the professionals at Grand Oriental Rug Gallery to handle all your rug servicing needs! We make sure that all necessary work is undertaken from start to finish, and assess for each rug the best cleaning method to suit its individual needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA few more reasons to hire us include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Experience – With years of experience coupled with the thousands of carpets we have serviced throughout the years, we have seen many different situations. And while we have yet to see it all, we have seen almost everything when it comes to rug cleaning and restoration. That said, when it comes to care and restoration of oriental rugs, we will make sure that your rugs are returned in better condition than when your rug first arrives at our facility, and our experience will allow us to make sure we are using what works best on various materials.</li><li>Affordable – We offer reasonable and affordable rates to our clients. However, there is no standard rate we asses. Each rug is evaluated on a case-by-case basis when it arrives to our facility, and many factors are considered when calculating a price. Some primary points that will help to determine the price range are: size, age (estimated, or for how long owned), area/country of origin, last instance of cleaning, composition and material, issues of concern.</li><li>Wide variety of services – Not only do we handle washing and cleaning needs, but we also take care of any re-weaving, repair and restoration needs. We will inform you before cleaning your rugs if we discover any areas of concern and suggest any subsequent course of action.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is important to always make sure to carefully consider which rug cleaners in Key Biscayne you should hire. We at Grand Oriental Rug Gallery know the value and investment your Oriental rugs are, which is why we take great pride in what we do. Give us a call to discuss how we will be able to help you with all your rug cleaning needs. We offer pick-up and delivery service Monday through Saturday.<br>Simply call 305 442 4500 or 305 490 1936.<br>A small town located on a barrier island, the Village of Key Biscayne is a must-see on any Miami visit. Located among Crandon Park and Bill Briggs State Park, Key Biscayne features elegant hotels, scenic beaches, and the famous Miami Seaquarium. Tourists and locals alike enjoy the beauty of Key Biscayne, and joggers and bicyclists can marvel the panoramic view off the Rickenbacker Causeway.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Key Biscayne','','inherit','closed','closed','','620-autosave-v1','','','2019-12-17 04:10:32','2019-12-17 04:10:32','',620,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/620-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(848,1,'2019-12-17 04:23:27','2019-12-17 04:23:27','','rug-pad-1','Rug & Carpet Pads','inherit','open','closed','','rug-pad-1','','','2019-12-19 21:27:22','2019-12-19 21:27:22','',587,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rug-pad-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(849,1,'2019-12-17 04:23:29','2019-12-17 04:23:29','','rug-pad-2','Carpet Rug Pads in grey','inherit','open','closed','','rug-pad-2','','','2019-12-23 04:23:38','2019-12-23 04:23:38','',587,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rug-pad-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(850,1,'2019-12-17 04:23:30','2019-12-17 04:23:30','','rug-pad-3','Rug pad','inherit','open','closed','','rug-pad-3','','','2019-12-23 04:23:17','2019-12-23 04:23:17','',587,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rug-pad-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(851,1,'2019-12-17 04:23:30','2019-12-17 04:23:30','','rug-pad-4','Rug pad','inherit','open','closed','','rug-pad-4','','','2019-12-20 03:25:44','2019-12-20 03:25:44','',587,'http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rug-pad-4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(852,1,'2019-12-17 04:25:05','2019-12-17 04:25:05','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Rug Pad – Carpet Pads</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s for the life and durability of your Oriental rug by absorbing much of the shock, pressure and